><p style="text-align: center;">Fri, Sep 3, 2021, 11:49â€¯PM</p><p style="text-align: center;">to Wendy</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">I wanted you so bad in this life and the next. But it looks like God has other plans. We are now broken up Wendy. Have a good rest of your life, however long that will be.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Love,</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Wendell Charles NeSmith</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p style="text-align: center;">Sun, Sep 5, 2021, 7:01â€¯PM</p><p style="text-align: center;">to Thomas, Ruby, Chris, Geoff</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">FYI</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Geoff Ward <geoffw@cahma.org.au></p><p style="text-align: center;">Mon, Sep 6, 2021, 9:58â€¯AM</p><p style="text-align: center;">to Wendell</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Dear Wendell,</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Sorry to hear this news. Hope you are OK.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Geoff</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">Sent from my Galaxy</p><p style="text-align: center;">...</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">[Message clipped]Â  View entire message</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">MOST WORSHIPFUL BROTHER YESHUA HAMASHIACH <bardpresident@gmail.com></p><p style="text-align: center;">Wed, Dec 24, 10:23â€¯AM (5 days ago)</p><p style="text-align: center;">to Wendy</p><p style="text-align: center;"><br /></p><p style="